---
description: Rules for curating resource entries in this repository
globs:
  - "content/**/*.md"
  - "content/**/*.yml"
alwaysApply: false
---

- Prefer practical AI builder resources over generic AI news or hype.
- Keep one resource per folder under `content/`.
- Include both `README.md` and `meta.yml` for resource entries.
- Write short summaries that explain why the resource matters.
- Avoid duplicate resources unless there is a clear distinction.
